sect1.para:
To view properties of a PGP key:




		Select the PGP key 
		from the main window,





		Double click on it or choose Properties 
		from the toolbar,





		Select the Details tab.

sect2.para:
If the chosen image is not of the required file type or size &app; 
can resize and convert it on the fly from 
any image format supported by the GDK library.

